      <title>中国在台湾附近开始更多的演习，向我们推回我们</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/china-holds-more-drills-near-taiwan-stepping-up-pressure-on-lai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，它正在台湾周围举行更多的军事演习，以阻止“分离主义力量”＆mdash;在美国发誓要阻止北京在该地区的侵略之后的举动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/china-holds-more-drills-near-taiwan-stepping-up-pressure-on-lai</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 23:53:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大关税之后，中国的养鱼者面临较高的粮食成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/china-s-fish-farmers-face-higher-food-costs-after-canada-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[鱼类食品可能是世界争夺贸易的世界中最晦涩的伤亡之一，破坏了从北美大草原到中国河流，湖泊和三角洲的数千个养鱼场的供应链。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/china-s-fish-farmers-face-higher-food-costs-after-canada-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 23:27:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，他会带回不太严格的汽车排放标准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-says-he-ll-return-less-stringent-auto-emissions-standards</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，他希望恢复较弱的汽车排放标准，将前总统乔·拜登（Joe Biden）施加的车辆污染路线对汽车制造商来说太繁重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-says-he-ll-return-less-stringent-auto-emissions-standards</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 23:08:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国迫使1000家公司在黑客之后进行网络辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/uk-to-compel-1-000-firms-to-shore-up-cyber-defenses-after-hacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府将通过立法迫使公司为关键的国家基础设施提供IT服务，以改善其网络防御，并在俄罗斯，中国，伊朗和朝鲜发动攻击之后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/uk-to-compel-1-000-firms-to-shore-up-cyber-defenses-after-hacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚反对派希望银行监管机构释放贷款规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/australia-opposition-wants-bank-regulator-to-ease-loan-standards</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚的中央反对派将敦促美国的银行监管机构缓解其抵押贷款标准，以便允许更多的人在下个月赢得办公室的情况下借用房屋。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/australia-opposition-wants-bank-regulator-to-ease-loan-standards</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 22:33:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国汽车制造商发疯，说服特朗普降级关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-automakers-lobby-to-exclude-low-cost-car-parts-from-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国汽车制造商正在做最后的努力，以在本周将生效的关税上席卷特朗普政府，并认为他们在国外采购的数千个部分可能会对该行业产生灾难性影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-automakers-lobby-to-exclude-low-cost-car-parts-from-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 21:32:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主党人起诉特朗普关于他的“选举诚信”秩序</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-sued-over-order-to-require-proof-of-citizenship-to-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的行政命令指导美国注册选民的方式进行重大变化，并将邮寄选票挑战为违宪的，这是民主党全国委员会和一组非营利组织提起的单独诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-sued-over-order-to-require-proof-of-citizenship-to-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 20:36:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈佛受到特朗普威胁，有90亿美元的危险资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-administration-to-review-billions-in-grants-to-harvard</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的政府扩大了反对精英大学的竞选活动，威胁要仔细研究为哈佛大学的数十亿美元的联邦资金，这是在冻结哥伦比亚大学的几周后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-administration-to-review-billions-in-grants-to-harvard</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 19:48:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金签证重置诱惑富裕的新西兰作为避风港</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/golden-visa-revamp-tempts-wealthy-to-eye-new-zealand-as-haven</link>
      <description><![CDATA[移民部长埃里卡·斯坦福（Erica Stanford）说，随着地缘政治紧张局势的上升促使富人考虑国外的选择，新西兰正在对其对美国和欧洲进行改造的黄金签证计划的“红热”兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/golden-visa-revamp-tempts-wealthy-to-eye-new-zealand-as-haven</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国制裁更多的香港官员在中国的镇压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-sanctions-more-hong-kong-officials-amid-beijing-led-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府正在批准六名中国和香港官员，包括该市司法部长和警察专员，以针对实施北京强硬政策的当局的最新步骤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-sanctions-more-hong-kong-officials-amid-beijing-led-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 17:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
